-- Montezemolo Sustains Second Monti Term, Corrier
-- B y   T o m m a s o   E b h a r d t
-- 2012-09-30T09:21:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-30/montezemolo-sustains-second-monti-term-corrier.html
Ferrari Chairman Luca Cordero Di Montezemolo’s political movement “Italia Futura” will run in
elections to sustain second term for Premier Mario Monti,
Corriere della Sera reports, citing interview with Montezemolo.
* Montezemolo says he will commit himself in project without
“claiming any role or leadership”: Corriere  To contact the reporter on this story:
